{SOUTH has 9 points a a \H suit - good enough to make a 
Negative Double over EAST's 1\S overcall. 

But NORTH doesn't have \Hs, she has \Ss and \Ds, so she bids 1NT to show 
her \S stopper and a minimum opener.

SOUTH should pass.}

